    q_copy_participation --> q_copy_justification: copy justification_bits, previous_justified_checkpoint, current_justified_checkpoint, finalized_checkpoint
    q_copy_justification --> q_copy_sync: copy inactivity_scores, current_sync_committee, next_sync_committee
    q_copy_sync --> q_copy_execution: copy latest_execution_payload_header
    q_copy_execution --> q_copy_withdrawals: copy next_withdrawal_index, next_withdrawal_validator_index, historical_summaries
    q_copy_withdrawals --> q_copy_deposits: copy deposit_requests_start_index, deposit_balance_to_consume
    q_copy_deposits --> q_copy_exits: copy exit_balance_to_consume, earliest_exit_epoch
    q_copy_exits --> q_copy_consolidations: copy consolidation_balance_to_consume, earliest_consolidation_epoch
    q_copy_consolidations --> q_copy_pending: copy pending_deposits, pending_partial_withdrawals, pending_consolidations
